    dc:title "A new species of Cardiodectes Wilson C. B., 1917 (Copepoda: Siphonostomatoida Pennellidae) from Spinyjaw greeneye, Chlorophthalmus corniger Alcock, 1894 off the Indian Ocean" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146825>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146833>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146815>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146817>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146827>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146829>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146823>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146831> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146825>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Scanning electron micrographs of Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., ovigerous female, A, dorsal view of body anterior showing cephalic lobes, neck lobes and cephalic processes; B–C, cephalic processes (arrows); D, ventral view of body anterior; E–F, neck; G, Leg 3; H, legs 1 and 2. p—cephalic processes; dl—dorsal lobe; vl—ventral lobe; al—anterior lobe; pl—posterior lobe; n—neck; nl1—first neck lobe; nl2—second neck lobe; t—trunk; L1—leg 1; L2—leg 2; L3—leg 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146833>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Scanning electron micrographs of Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., ovigerous female, A–B, trunk posterior showing genital orifice (arrow); C–D, trunk posterior showing egg sac (arrow)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146815>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Attachment sites of mature post-metamorphic adult females of Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., on Spinyjaw greeneye, Chlorophthalmus corniger Alcock, 1894. A, on the upper and lower jaws (arrows); B, on the dorsal and dorso-lateral body surface between eyes and dorsal fin (arrows); C, dorsal surface of the host’s head, carrying the parasite which induced a swelling on the head (arrow); D, lateral body surface (arrows)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146815/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146817>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., mature post-metamorphic adult females. A–B, paratype (preserved)(Reg. No. ZSI/WGRC/IR/ INV/ 25194) dorso-lateral and ventral views; C, holotype (fresh)(Reg. No. ZSI/WGRC/IR/ INV/ 25193); D, paratype (fresh)(Reg. No. ZSI/WGRC/IR/ INV/ 25196)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146827>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., matured post-metamorphic adult female, A, antennule; B, antenna; C, maxillule; D, maxilla; E, leg 1 with inter-coxal sclerite; F, leg 2 with inter-coxal sclerite; G, legs 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146829>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., matured post-metamorphic adult female, A–B, antennule and antenna; C, antennule showing setae (arrows); D–F, antenna (arrow). a1—antennule; a2—antenna; s—seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146823>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., A–C, dorsal, ventral and lateral views of ovigerous female paratype (Reg. No. ZSI/WGRC/IR/ INV/ 25194)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10146831>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Cardiodectes vampire sp. nov., matured post-metamorphic adult female, A, legs 1 and 2; B, leg 1 with plumose setae and spine; C–D, legs 1 and 2 with inter-coxal sclerite. ps—plumose setae; s—seta; ex—exopod; en—endopod; st—coxal sclerite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10146831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

